# install Chocolaty

1. Run Powershell as Administrator
2. `Set-ExecutionPolicy Bypass -Scope Process -Force; [System.Net.ServicePointManager]::SecurityProtocol = [System.Net.ServicePointManager]::SecurityProtocol -bor 3072; iex ((New-Object System.Net.WebClient).DownloadString('https://community.chocolatey.org/install.ps1'))`
3. Note: To confirm automatically next time, use '-y' or consider:
choco feature enable -n allowGlobalConfirmation

# install
1. powertoys - advanced features, used for remapping keys
  - any way to script keybinds? 
    - ctrl (L) -> alt (L), alt (L) -> ctrl (L) --> adjust keyboard to be similar to mac cmd key
    - capslock -> ctrl --> keybind for vim
  - shortcuts
    - ctrl (L) -> alt (L) --> allows for alt-tab functionality with new keybinds
